########### Run task 1 experiment ###########

You need to install pytorch

conda create --name beetl python=3.8 anaconda=2021.05
conda install pytorch==1.8.1 torchvision torchaudio cudatoolkit=10.2 -c pytorch

conda activate beetl

Install necessary package in the requirement.txt

pip install -r requirements.tx

1) Download the necessary data

https://github.com/XiaoxiWei/NeurIPS_BEETL/blob/main/start_kits/1.LeaderboardDataGuide.ipynb
The source motor imagery data is downloaded with Moabb

Put all the data under EEG_Lightning/da_dataset

EEG_Lightning/da_dataset/finalMI  (this is for final motor imagery)
EEG_Lightning/da_dataset/SleepSource/SleepSource (this is for the source dataset in sleep data)
EEG_Lightning/da_dataset/finalSleep/sleep_target (this is for final target dataset in sleep data
EEG_Lightning/da_dataset/finalSleep/testing (this is for final test dataset in sleep data)

2) generate data format

go to EEG_Lightning/submission to run python generate_task_1_data.py


The matlab data is generated in the directory EEG_Lightning/da_dataset/task_1/

3) The experiment is located in EEG_Lightning/submission/task_1

4) run the training script

EEG_Lightning/submission/task_1_script to run source task_1_script.sh

define the location of the train scrip

computer_dir="C:/wduong_folder/Dassl.pytorch-master/NeurIPS_competition/EEG_Lightning/"
computer_dir is where you store the directory EEG_Lightning


5) Generate predict file

Go to EEG_Lightning/submission to run process_predict_task_1.py

The .txt file with the test data prediction is generated in the folder EEG_Lightning/submission/util/task_1/answer.txt


########### Run task 2 experiment ###########


2) generate data format

go to EEG_Lightning/submission to run python generate_task_2_data.py

To get source dasets, we use moabb

Put the target dataset under EEG_Lightning/da_dataset
EEG_Lightning/da_dataset/finalMI  (this is for final motor imagery)

3) The experiment is located in EEG_Lightning/submission/task_1

4) run the training script

EEG_Lightning/submission/task_2_script to run       source task_2_script.sh

define the location of the train scrip

computer_dir="C:/wduong_folder/Dassl.pytorch-master/NeurIPS_competition/EEG_Lightning/"
computer_dir is where you store the directory EEG_Lightning


5) Generate predict file

Go to EEG_Lightning/submission to run process_predict_task_2.py

The .txt file with the test data prediction is generated in the folder EEG_Lightning/submission/util/task_2/answer.txt




